{"id":580,"date":"2024-08-02T18:54:50","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T18:54:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=580"},"modified":"2024-08-02T18:54:50","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T18:54:50","slug":"tm030-shadow-ball","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm030-shadow-ball\/","title":{"rendered":"TM030 Shadow Ball"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM030 Shadow Ball<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>On an island on Route 9 in the middle of the lake.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>A shadowy blob is hurled at the foe. It may also lower the foe\u2019s special defense.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>15<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Ghost<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Tehl Town<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Starting from the Tehl Town Pok\u00e9mon Center, go to the South-West edge of the town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-tehl-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Tehl Town Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Tehl Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Follow the West path out of the town and continue on the path as you enter Route 9.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-exiting-tehl-town.jpg\" alt=\"Exiting Tehl Town. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Exiting Tehl Town.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you can, start following the path North, walking past the Chansey.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-walking-toward-the-chansey.jpg\" alt=\"Walking toward the Chansey. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking toward the Chansey.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually come across a crossroad where you want to go West.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-west-when-possible.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path West when possible. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path West when possible.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start Surfing North just before walking past the Bug Catcher NPC.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-go-north-before-passing-the-bug-catcher-npc.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to go North before passing the Bug Catcher NPC. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Surf to go North before passing the Bug Catcher NPC.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep going North on the water and the TM for Shadow Ball will be on the second island you see.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-shadow-ball.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Shadow Ball. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Shadow Ball.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":581,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-580","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/580","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/581"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=580"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=580"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}